  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Season veal cutlets with salt, black pepper, and Kenyan chili flakes.",
    "Grill the veal cutlets for 3 minutes per side or until cooked through.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together lamb's breast fat, garlic, cilantro, parsley, red pepper flakes, and lemon juice.",
    "Brush the mixture onto the grilled veal cutlets.",
    "Top the veal cutlets with cheddar cheese, scallions, and chili peppers.",
    "Place the veal cutlets back on the grill for another 2 minutes or until the cheese is melted and bubbly.",
    "Remove the veal cutlets from the grill and top with yak butter and fresh cilantro.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!",
    "Serve with a side of steamed vegetables or a salad for a well-rounded meal.",
    "For a spicy kick, add more Kenyan chili flakes or red pepper flakes to taste."
